*gnomemeeting-1.2.2 (12 Sep 2005)

  12 Sep 2005; Stefan Knoblich <stkn@gentoo.org>
  +files/gnomemeeting-1.2.2-dbus.diff, +gnomemeeting-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Version bump and cleanups.

  29 Jul 2005; <stkn@gentoo.org> gnomemeeting-1.2.1.ebuild,
  gnomemeeting-1.2.0.ebuild:
  -O3 causes trouble with audio plugins, replace with -O2
  (bug #88710).

  27 Jul 2005; Pieter Van den Abeele <pvdabeel@gentoo.org>
  gnomemeeting-1.2.0.ebuild, gnomemeeting-1.2.1.ebuild:
  Stable mask. This version has Howl support (Gnome version of
  mdns/zeroconf/bonjour) and detects people on the intranet using
  Gnomemeeting. Also, this is the target for testing Altivec optimized
  Openh323 in the Freescale DES.

  11 Apr 2005; Stefan Knoblich <stkn@gentoo.org>
  +files/gnomemeeting-1.2.1-configure.patch, gnomemeeting-1.2.1.ebuild:
  Fix bug #88711, install schema file into proper directories

  11 Apr 2005; Stefan Knoblich <stkn@gentoo.org> gnomemeeting-1.2.1.ebuild:
  Fixed depends.

